      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs traceable to measured data; input uncertainty characterized.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus (114 ± 3 GPa) and yield strength (880 ± 15 MPa) sourced from coupon testing of production-lot material. Screw geometry digitized from CMM measurements of three production screws. Input uncertainty is propagated through the validation metric uval. All input values are traceable to calibrated measurement records."
    },
    {
