      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions replicate the F1717 test fixture geometry. Screw geometry used in simulation was derived from CMM measurements of the same production lot as the tested constructs. Material property inputs are within one standard deviation of measured coupon values. Equivalency is formally documented in the validation plan."
    },
